OL,3,CSchools reopen after testing for
OL,4,Casbestos in play sand
OL,6,FSchools on North Tyneside that were
OL,7,Fshut to allow for further tests to be
OL,8,Fcarried out for asbestos in play sand
OL,9,Fhave now all reopened.
OL,11,FNorth Tyneside Council confirmed on
OL,12,FMonday (18 May) that Beacon Hill
OL,13,FSchool, in Wallsend, had reopened
OL,14,Ffollowing a negative test result.
OL,16,FIt was one of four settings affected
OL,17,Fby closures, which followed a report
OL,18,Ffrom Whitley Lodge First School, in
OL,19,FWhitley Bay, where asbestos was found
OL,20,Fto be present in play sand.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
