OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1779120673
OL,3,CSchools reopen after testing for
OL,4,Casbestos in play sand
OL,6,FWhitely Lodge First School, Woodlawn
OL,7,FSchool, in Whitley Bay, and Silverdale
OL,8,FSchool, in Wallsend, were all subject
OL,9,Fto full or partial closures to allow
OL,10,Ffor testing, and have all fully
OL,11,Freopened.
OL,13,FConcerns about asbestos followed a
OL,14,Fnational product recall of almost 40
OL,15,Fitems sold by supermarkets and high
OL,16,Fstreet stores.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
