OL,3,CSchools reopen after testing for
OL,4,Casbestos in play sand
OL,6,FRebecca Wall, Director of Childrens
OL,7,FServices at North Tyneside Council,
OL,8,Fsaid: "All North Tyneside schools
OL,9,Faffected have now reopened following a
OL,10,Fnegative result from advanced asbestos
OL,11,Ftesting at Beacon Hill School.
OL,13,F"The advice to all schools and
OL,14,Fsettings with play sand remains to
OL,15,Fkeep it covered for the time being and
OL,16,Fcheck the brand against the published
OL,17,Fproduct recall list on the Office for
OL,18,FProduct Safety and Standards website.
